  <!-- =========================================================================
       Description — plain <p> paragraphs; no markup beyond <em>, <code>, <ul>/<li>
       ========================================================================= -->
  <description>
    <p>
      Real Vibecode is an AI-native IDE built on a forked architecture, combining
      the power of an AI execution kernel with a proven code editor foundation.
    </p>
    <p>
      It provides an authoritative mutation control layer and a causal execution
      graph engine for transparent, auditable AI-driven development. Every AI
      action is tracked, replayable, and reversible — giving developers full
      control over autonomous coding workflows.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI Execution Kernel with autonomous code editing and multi-agent orchestration</li>
      <li>Causal Execution Graph for full traceability and replay of AI actions</li>
      <li>Transactional Edit System with rollback and verification</li>
      <li>Repository Intelligence with codebase-aware context optimization</li>
      <li>Terminal Integration with AI-assisted command safety</li>
      <li>Cost Governor for managing AI provider token usage</li>
      <li>Built-in LLM provider support with streaming output</li>
      <li>MCP (Model Context Protocol) integration for extensible AI tooling</li>
      <li>Rich extension ecosystem compatible with VS Code extensions</li>
      <li>Integrated terminal, debugger, and Git workflow support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

